data.description:
AVAILABLE SOON! Built new in 2017, perfectly blending elegance with functional living space.
Excellent 1BR/1BA floor plan with custom upgrades, including Elfa shelving
throughout, additional cable and power outlets in living room and bedroom for TV
mounts, and matte black bathroom hardware with stylish vanity backsplash.
Open living room and kitchen with stainless steel appliances and ample cabinet space.
Bedroom is 10’ x 11’ with a remote-controlled/lighted ceiling fan and fits up to a queen-sized bed with plenty of remaining space for 1 or 2 nightstands.
This gorgeous modern condo features energy efficient LED lighting, quartz
countertops, full-sized washer/dryer with Elfa shelving, and hardwood
flooring throughout. Bus stop just steps away and 4 blocks to Stadium Armory Metro station.
This property boasts ground level front and rear access, community gas grill and bike
rack, and quick access to trash/recycling bins. HOA dues are $246/mo which includes
trash/recycling, gas, and water. Average electric bill is just $40/month
Bus stop just steps away, 4 blocks to Metro rail where just 3 stops to Capital South
and 2 additional stops to L’Enfant Plaza with yellow/green line transfers.Don't miss your chance to own in this beautiful, one-owner, Lock 7 condominium! Just two blocks from Lincoln Park, this Capitol Hill property was owned new January 2018! Elegant, contemporary finishes include gourmet kitchens w/quartz counters, SS appliances w/gas cooking, nest thermostats, custom Elfa closets throughout, full size front-loading W/D, wired for security systems. This unit boasts abundant storage and sits at ground level offering swift street access to the front and rear.  Call to arrange a showing. Open House coming soon!
data.whatILove: Proximity to everything DC has to offer without having to fight for a parking spot   Street parking is always available in this up and coming neighborhood!   If they continue to build up the area around RFK stadium this condo will go from great to unbeatable!
